{
  "frontCover": "Front cover of a greeting card with a 9:16 ratio, featuring a \"Dreamy Fantasy\" anime style. The background is a deep purple-blue night sky filled with soft, twinkling stars and abstract, wispy clouds in pastel pinks and blues. Floating in the upper left are luminous, translucent jellyfish-like creatures with delicate tendrils. In the upper right, a stylized, swirled planet with pastel colors is visible. The central focus is on two \"whimsical characters\" with \"simplified, friendly features\" riding on the back of a fluffy, white, moth-like creature with large, bright blue eyes and iridescent, feather-like wings. The character on the left has dark, curly hair, is winking, and wearing a black top with a geometric pattern in white. The character on the right has light brown hair, wears a beanie and an orange shirt, and is pointing excitedly upwards with their tongue sticking out playfully. The text \"Happy Birthday Sunny\" is written in a beautiful, flowing, \"handwritten cursive script\" in a soft yellow-golden color, positioned centrally and clearly readable, avoiding the top and bottom 10% edges. The overall mood is \"quirky,\" \"unique,\" and \"magical,\" with a \"soft\" and \"enchanting\" atmosphere.",
  "backCover": "Back cover of a greeting card with a 9:16 ratio, in a \"Dreamy Fantasy\" anime style consistent with the front. The background is a continuation of the starry purple-blue night sky, but rendered more simply, with scattered soft stars and subtle pastel cloud wisps. In the center-left area, there are faint, luminous outlines of the same jellyfish-like creatures from the front cover, appearing more ethereal. The \"fluffy, white, moth-like creature\" from the front is subtly suggested as a faint, luminescent outline or a gentle, soft texture flowing across the bottom, with hints of its iridescent wings. The right bottom corner, approximately 1 inch square, is left completely clear and undecorated for a QR code. The overall design is \"minimal\" and \"serene,\" offering a \"peaceful closure\" with \"unexpected artistic elements\" that echo the front cover's magic without being overly detailed or complex. The mood is calming and subtly enchanting.",
  "leftInterior": "Left interior of a greeting card with a 9:16 ratio, in a \"Dreamy Fantasy\" anime style. The background depicts a \"magical atmosphere\" with a swirling nebula of \"soft pastels\" in blues, purples, and pinks. \"Detailed nature elements\" include clusters of glowing, bioluminescent flowers with delicate, almost crystalline petals scattered across the scene, and stylized, translucent, floating dandelion seeds or spore-like particles drifting through the air. The composition evokes a sense of wonder and exploration. The \"quirky\" and \"unique\" tone is conveyed through the unexpected combination of cosmic and organic elements. There are no people or characters on this page. The overall visual is \"innovative\" and \"surprising,\" setting a \"dreamlike\" mood.",
  "rightInterior": "Right interior of a greeting card with a 9:16 ratio, in a \"Dreamy Fantasy\" anime style consistent with the other panels. The background is a blend of \"soft pastels\" forming a cosmic, ethereal landscape with swirling clouds and distant stars. The \"message text: \"Sunny, another year of orbiting the sun together and you're still my favorite weirdo in the entire galaxy. They say wisdom comes with age, but I'm glad we've just gotten better at being ridiculous. Here's to another trip around the big fiery star, my friend. Happy Birthday from your partner-in-shenanigans, Rana\"\" is rendered in a \"beautiful, clearly readable handwritten cursive script\" in a warm, golden-yellow ink, appearing as if written with a \"nice pen-style appearance\" with natural ink flow and slight variations in line weight. The text is \"integrated into beautiful, innovative decorative artwork\" that frames it without overpowering it. This artwork consists of delicate, luminous celestial vines that weave around the text, interspersed with shimmering stars and soft, glowing orbs that resemble distant galaxies or magical fireflies. The \"enchanting fairy-tale\" quality is emphasized, creating an \"emotional peak\" that is both heartfelt and visually captivating. The overall tone is \"unique\" and \"unconventional.\""
}
